      <title>尽管选举导致波动，美国银行仍看好卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/bank-of-america-bullish-on-rupee-despite-election-led-volatility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管未来市场波动性指标因印度选举而上升，但美国银行仍维持对印度卢比的看涨看法。]]></description>
